value: Um… If you have a moment to talk! …They left…
Although I attempt to stir conversation､ it’s so loud that I cannot converse without shouting…
I cannot obtain a chance to begin conversation. Just as I thought､ a place of this sort seems too difficult for me…
Kurou-chan､ you havin’ fun~? Let’s play darts over here together~!
Darts… is it? Erm､ this is… similar to that of Tousenkyou､ isn’t it?
All I need to do is throw it? …There.
Whoa!? You hit the center!? All three of them､ too!! You sure are awesome､ Kurou-chan!!
I heard that dude rocking those traditional clothes is showin’ off real good with the darts over there!!
Ooh､ you seem like a pretty stiff guy､ but when we actually get talkin’ with you､ you’re actually real considerate! Bro!
Why､ thank you… For some reason or another､ I’ve become surrounded by a great number of people.
